      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 2.12,
      "endTime": 8.67
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_3",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "What was the consequence of the editor's insistence on facts and statistics?",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 8.68,
      "endTime": 16.64,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "What",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "什么"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_4",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Editors of newspapers and magazines often go to extremes to provide their readers with unimportant facts and statistics.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 16.65,
      "endTime": 25,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s1",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Last year a journalist had been instructed by a well-known magazine to write an article on the president's palace in a new African republic.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 25.01,
      "endTime": 35.08
    },
    {
      "id": "s2",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "When the article arrived, the editor read the first sentence and then refused to publish it.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 35.09,
      "endTime": 42.42,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s3",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The article began:'Hundreds of steps lead to the high wall which surrounds the president's palace.'",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 42.43,
      "endTime": 50.23
    },
    {
      "id": "s4",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "The editor at once sent the journalist a fax instructing him to find out the exact number of steps and the height of the wall.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 50.24,
      "endTime": 61.27,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          },
          {
            "word": "Number",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "号码，数字"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s5",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The journalist immediately set out to obtain these important facts, but he took a long time to send them.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 61.28,
      "endTime": 68.65
    },
    {
      "id": "s6",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Meanwhile, the editor was getting impatient, for the magazine would soon go to press.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 68.66,
      "endTime": 74.23
    },
    {
      "id": "s7",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "He sent the journalist two more faxes, but received no reply.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 74.24,
      "endTime": 79.43
    },
    {
      "id": "s8",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "He sent yet another fax informing the journalist that if he did not reply soon he would be fired.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 79.44,
      "endTime": 86.8,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s9",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "When the journalist again failed to reply,  the editor reluctantly published the article as it had originally been written.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 86.81,
      "endTime": 95.6,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s10",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "A week later, the editor at last received a fax from the journalist.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 95.61,
      "endTime": 100.97,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s11",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Not only had the poor man been arrested, but he had been sent to prison as well.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 100.98,
      "endTime": 107.18,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          },
          {
            "word": "Man",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "男人"
          },
          {
            "word": "Well",
            "pos": "adj.",
            "meaning": "健康的，良好的"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s12",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "However, he had at last been allowed to send a fax in which he informed the editor that he had been arrested",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 107.19,
      "endTime": 115.98,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          },
          {
